summary:
Add 3 chests for Warrior, Mage, Thief at the guardian stones near Riverwood.
Inside containing Items for Warrior, Mage and Thief.
descriptionHtml:
Just a headstart mod if you don't want to play Skyrim the second time and need to find everything again.

This will add three chests with goodies and whatever you might need in the start of the game.
The chests will be located at the Guardian Stones near Riverwood.

I wouldn't call this a "cheat mod" because it more like a give from the "Guardians".

To Do-list
-Make chests only open when activating the corresponding stone. (Thieve Stone for Thief's Chest)
author: Krongfah
